<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Fallback background color */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden; /* Prevent scrollbars if content is centered */
        }

        /* Background Image on Body */
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/LaptopSize.png'); /* Default background */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            transition: background-image 0.3s ease-in-out, filter 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        /* Responsive Background Images */
        @@media (max-width: 576px) { /* Small phones */
            body {
                background-image: url('/images/PhoneSize.png');
            }
        }

        @@media (min-width: 577px) and (max-width: 768px) { /* Large phones */
            body {
                background-image: url('/images/LargePhone.png');
            }
        }

        @@media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) { /* Tablets */
            body {
                background-image: url('/images/IPadSize.png');
            }
        }

        @@media (min-width: 1025px) { /* Laptops and larger screens */
            body {
                background-image: url('/images/LaptopSize.png');
            }
        }

        /* Order Section */
        .order-section {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 1;
            width: 90%; /* Default width */
            max-width: 500px; /* Limit width for larger screens */
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding in width calculations */
        }

        .order-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5; /* Better readability */
        }

        .order-section a.order-now {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background-color: #ffdd57;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .order-section a.order-now:hover {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        center a {
            display: none;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-evenly;">
        <!-- Order Section -->
        <div class="order-section">
            <p>هذا الموقع مخصص لطلب البطاقات والدوسيات، بالإضافة إلى عرض تفاصيل العروض المتاحة.</p>
            <a class="order-now" asp-action="Shop" asp-controller="Home" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;">اطلب الآن</a>
            <a class="login-admin" asp-action="Login" asp-controller="Account" style="display: block; margin-top: 15px; color: white;">تسجيل الدخول (للادمن فقط)</a>
        </div>
        <div class="order-section" style="margin-top:50px;">
            <a class="order-now" class="login-admin" asp-action="Search" asp-controller="Home">الاسعلام عن طلبي</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
